Job Title: Software Engineer – Fresh Graduate
Location: Islamabad, Pakistan
Company: TechNova Solutions Pvt. Ltd.
Department: Engineering
Job Type: Full-Time
Reports To: Engineering Manager

About the Role
TechNova Solutions is excited to welcome a passionate and motivated Software Engineer (Fresh Graduate) to join our dynamic engineering team. This role offers a fantastic opportunity for recent graduates to kickstart their careers by working on real-world projects, learning from experienced developers, and growing their software development skills in a supportive environment.

Key Responsibilities
Collaborate with senior engineers to design, develop, test, and deploy software applications

Write clean, maintainable, and efficient code following best practices

Participate in code reviews and contribute to team knowledge sharing

Debug, troubleshoot, and resolve software defects

Assist in the documentation of software designs, processes, and user guides

Continuously learn new technologies and improve programming skills

Work with cross-functional teams including QA, product management, and design

Qualifications
Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, or related field (fresh graduates welcome)

Basic knowledge of programming languages such as Java, Python, C#, or JavaScript

Understanding of software development lifecycle (SDLC) and Agile methodologies

Familiarity with version control tools (e.g., Git)

Strong problem-solving skills and a willingness to learn

Good communication and teamwork abilities

Passion for technology and software development

Preferred (Not Required)
Internship or project experience in software development

Familiarity with web frameworks or databases

Exposure to cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or Google Cloud

What We Offer
Structured onboarding and mentorship program

Opportunities for professional growth and certifications

Friendly and collaborative work environment

Competitive starting salary

Health insurance and paid leave benefits

How to Apply
Send your CV and a cover letter to careers@technova.pk with the subject line:
Software Engineer – Fresh Graduate – [Your Name]
Deadline for applications: July 20, 2025
